o La Tengo</a>为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-wilco-join-yo-la-tengo-to-cover-the-beatles-bob-dylan-at-chicago-show-3420563">他们在芝加哥 Metro 的演出加演</a>了 Wilco，贯穿了<a href="/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队的</a>《She&#39;s A Woman》、<a href="/artists/bob-dylan">鲍勃·迪伦</a>的《Love Minus Zero/No Limit》、The Heartbreakers 的《Love Minus Zero/No Limit》。 “One Track Mind”和 Fairport Convention 的“谁知道时间都去哪儿了？”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wilcos-jeff-tweedy-i-tried-to-be-a-rock-critic-but-i-couldnt-do-it-3566391">Wilco 的 Jeff Tweedy 的帖子：“我试图成为一名摇滚评论家，但我做不到”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
凯莉·克拉克森谈到离婚后的抑郁症“异常艰难” https://www.nme.com/news/music/kelly-clarkson-speaks-about-extraordinarily-hard-post-divorce-depression-3566394?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=kelly-clarkson-speaks-about-extraordinarily-离婚后的艰难抑郁症Max PilleyFri, 05 Jan 2024 20:45:08 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3566394 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kelly_clarkson_2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯莉·克拉克森" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kelly_clarkson_2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kelly_clarkson_2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kelly_clarkson_2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kelly_clarkson_2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kelly_clarkson_2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kelly_clarkson_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位歌手于 2013 年至 2022 年间与她的前经纪人布兰登·布莱克斯托克 (Brandon Blackstock) 结婚</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kelly-clarkson-speaks-about-extraordinarily-hard-post-divorce-depression-3566394">凯莉·克拉克森 (Kelly Clarkson) 谈到离婚后抑郁症“异常艰难”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kelly_clarkson_2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯莉·克拉克森" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kelly_clarkson_2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kelly_clarkson_2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kelly_clarkson_2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kelly_clarkson_2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kelly_clarkson_2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kelly_clarkson_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kelly-clarkson">凯莉·克拉克森</a>公开讲述了她最近离婚后经历的“异常艰难”的抑郁症。</p><p>这位歌手于 2013 年至 2022 年间与她的前经纪人、娱乐制作人布兰登·布莱克斯托克 (Brandon Blackstock) 结婚，并育有两个孩子：9 岁的 River Rose 和 7 岁的雷明顿 (Remington)。</p><p>她在接受<a href="https://people.com/kelly-clarkson-on-working-through-depression-extraordinarily-hard-divorce-taking-power-back-exclusive-8421288" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《人物》</em></a>杂志采访时描述了为最新专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kelly-clarkson-announces-new-album-chemistry-3420794">Chemistry</a> 》创作音乐如何迫使她面对离婚后的情感动荡。 </p><figure id="attachment_3443621" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3443621" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3443621" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Kelly-Clarkson@2000x1270.jpg" alt="凯莉·克拉克森 (Kelly Clarkson) 在 2023 年 iHeartRadio 音乐奖上表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Kelly-Clarkson@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Kelly-Clarkson@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Kelly-Clarkson@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Kelly-Clarkson@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Kelly-Clarkson@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Kelly-Clarkson@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3443621" class="wp-caption-text">凯莉·克拉克森。图片来源：杰夫·克拉维茨/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>“我无法表达我对拥有这种健康出路的感激之情，”她说。 “因为抑郁症以及离婚或悲伤带来的事情非常困难。你会感到孤独，能够有一个发泄那些压倒性情绪的出口真是一件幸事。”</p><p> “这听起来很有治疗作用，但那是因为我喜欢治疗，而且我认为拥有这些工具来引导你的生活和人际关系很重要。”</p><p>克拉克森<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kelly-clarkson-announces-new-album-chemistry-3420794">去年六月发行了她的第十张录音室专辑“Chemistry”</a> ，之后她在7月28日至8月19日期间进行了她在拉斯维加斯的首场驻场演出“Chemistry: An Intimate Evening with Kelly Clarkson”。</p><p>巡演的几次约会中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kelly-clarkson-warns-fans-against-throwing-things-onstage-at-las-vegas-residency-3476190">她责骂了一位在舞台上向她扔毛绒玩具的观众</a>。 “如果你要扔屎，那就扔钻石吧，”她说。</p><p>按照克拉克森以翻唱歌曲开场脱口秀的传统，她在 11 月打破了选择<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo</a> ) 和比莉·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">艾利什 (Billie Eilish)</a>等排行榜冠军<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kelly-clarkson-cover-bloc-party-like-eating-glass-3549963">歌手演唱 Bloc Party 2004 年歌曲《Like Eating Glass》的版本的习惯</a>。</p><p>她之前演绎另类经典的例子包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/watch-kelly-clarkson-cover-the-arctic-monkeys-do-i-wanna-know-on-kellyoke-3390045">Arctic Monkeys 的《Do I Wanna Know》、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kelly-clarkson-cover-all-the-small-things-blink-182-3379348">Blink-182 的《All The Small Things》、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/news/music/watch-kelly-clarkson-perform-soundgardens-black-hole-sun-on-the-kelly-clarkson-show-3339319">Soundgarden 的《Black Hole Sun》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kelly-clarkson-put-her-kellyoke-spin-on-the-smiths-how-soon-is-now-3221944">The Smiths 的《How Soon Is Now?》</a> ，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kelly-clarkson-cover-radioheads-exit-music-for-a-film-3213412">Radiohead 的“退出音乐（电影）”</a> 。</p><p>去年五月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kelly-clarkson-addresses-allegations-of-toxic-work-environment-on-her-talk-show-3443616">克拉克森在她的日间脱口秀节目中谈到了最近有关有毒工作环境的指控</a>，其中工作人员指责制片人“过度工作”和“支付过低工资”。</p><p> “我一直并将继续致力于在<i>凯利克拉克森秀</i>上创造和维护一个安全和健康的环境。当我们准备搬到东海岸时，我比以往任何时候都更加致力于确保我们正在搬迁的团队以及我们在纽约的新团队都由业内最优秀、最友善的人组成，”她说。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kelly-clarkson-speaks-about-extraordinarily-hard-post-divorce-depression-3566394">凯莉·克拉克森 (Kelly Clarkson) 谈到离婚后抑郁症“异常艰难”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
